contentrichtext.text: {{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}} The '''United Democratic Party''' is a [[political party]] in the [[Marshall Islands]]. At the last [[legislative]] [[elections in Marshall Islands|elections]], 17 November 2003, no parties participated, though part of the members could be members of either the [[Kabua Party]] or the United Democratic Party. {{Marshall Islands political parties}} [[Category:Political parties in the Marshall Islands]] {{Oceania-party-stub}} {{Marshalls-stub}}
